WEBVTT

00:01.702 --> 00:03.170
<i>PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i>ON "WAYWARD PINES"...</i>

00:03.170 --> 00:04.345
Ethan: WHERE AM I?

00:04.345 --> 00:07.069
Ruby: YOU'RE IN
WAYWARD PINES, IDAHO.

00:07.069 --> 00:08.236
IDAHO?

00:08.236 --> 00:09.905
COULD HAVE BEEN MUCH WORSE.

00:09.905 --> 00:11.706
IT WAS A NASTY CAR ACCIDENT.

00:12.908 --> 00:14.876
HELLO?
THERESA,
THERE'S BEEN AN ACCIDENT.

00:14.876 --> 00:18.113
SO, WHAT EXACTLY ARE YOU DOING
HERE, MR. SECRET AGENT MAN?

00:18.113 --> 00:20.148
MISSING PERSON'S
INVESTIGATION.

00:20.148 --> 00:22.317
Stallings:
DOES YOUR WIFE KNOW THAT ONE
OF THE MISSING AGENTS

00:22.317 --> 00:23.752
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR
IS KATE HEWSON?

00:23.752 --> 00:26.088
WHAT HAPPENED BETWEEN
KATE AND I, IT'S OVER.

00:26.088 --> 00:29.291
I FOLLOWED THE ADDRESS
THAT THE BARTENDER GAVE ME.

00:29.291 --> 00:31.860
AND THAT'S WHERE I FOUND
THE BODY OF MY COLLEAGUE.

00:31.860 --> 00:34.663
WHAT HAPPENED TO EVANS?
HE TRIED TO ESCAPE.

00:34.663 --> 00:36.798
I DON'T HAVE ANSWERS
FOR YOU, ETHAN.

00:36.798 --> 00:37.933
YOU SHOULD GO.

00:37.933 --> 00:39.067
KATE, I'M IN TROUBLE.

00:39.067 --> 00:40.235
THEY'RE WATCHING US.

00:40.235 --> 00:41.837
WHO?
Shh.

00:41.837 --> 00:42.804
And listening.

00:44.673 --> 00:48.176
ALL I WANT TO DO IS GET OUT
OF THIS ROTTEN, INSANE TOWN!
OKAY. OKAY. OKAY.

00:48.176 --> 00:50.645
IT'S JUST A TOWN.

00:59.688 --> 01:01.957
[ELECTRICITY BUZZING]

01:05.093 --> 01:07.329
YOU DIDN'T MAKE IT TOO FAR,
DID YOU?

01:07.329 --> 01:08.830
HOW DO I GET OUT OF HERE?

01:08.830 --> 01:10.132
YOU DON'T.

01:13.270 --> 01:15.472
PUT YOUR HANDS
ON TOP OF THE HOOD.

01:15.472 --> 01:17.708
LOOK,
I'M A GOVERNMENT AGENT.

01:17.708 --> 01:20.578
YEAH, AND MARY POPPINS
IS YOUR GRANDMOTHER.

01:20.578 --> 01:23.547
YOU'RE A GUY WITH NO I.D.,
NO BADGE,

01:23.547 --> 01:25.950
WHO JUST STOLE THAT CAR!

01:25.950 --> 01:27.718
YOU WANT TO MOVE THAT GUN?

01:27.718 --> 01:29.720
YEAH, GLADLY.

01:29.720 --> 01:30.955
[GROANS]

01:30.955 --> 01:33.724
YOU JUST ASSAULTED
A FEDERAL AGENT.

01:33.724 --> 01:35.359
NO.

01:35.359 --> 01:38.762
I JUST RESTRAINED A SUSPECT
WHO WAS RESISTING ARREST.

01:38.762 --> 01:39.897
GET UP ON YOUR FEET.

01:39.897 --> 01:41.565
[GROANS]

01:41.565 --> 01:44.869
YOU SEE, I CALLED THE SEATTLE
SECRET SERVICE OFFICE.

01:44.869 --> 01:46.437
THEY'VE NEVER HEARD OF YOU.

01:46.437 --> 01:48.472
WHO DID YOU TALK TO
OVER THERE?

01:48.472 --> 01:50.374
NEVER MIND
WHO WE TALKED TO.

01:50.374 --> 01:51.742
AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,

01:51.742 --> 01:53.878
YOU'RE STILL
MY NUMBER-ONE SUSPECT.

01:53.878 --> 01:56.513
LOOK, I DIDN'T KILL EVANS.

01:56.513 --> 01:58.682
I WAS SENT HERE TO FIND HIM.

01:58.682 --> 02:00.351
I CAN HELP YOU.

02:00.351 --> 02:02.786
I'VE GOT 15 YEARS OF LAW
ENFORCEMENT UNDER MY BELT.

02:02.786 --> 02:05.322
I DON'T CARE
WHAT YOU THINK YOU GOT!

02:05.322 --> 02:08.859
IF I WANT YOUR HELP,
I WILL ASK FOR IT.

02:08.859 --> 02:12.529
OTHERWISE, YOU STAY
IN THAT HOTEL ROOM.

02:12.529 --> 02:14.531
HEY, ALEX! LARRY!

02:14.531 --> 02:17.568
DON'T TRY TO LEAVE, MR. BURKE.

02:17.568 --> 02:19.904
THAT'S RULE NUMBER ONE.

03:15.259 --> 03:17.361
[CLOCK TICKING]

03:19.563 --> 03:22.399
[ALARM CLOCK RINGS]

03:26.737 --> 03:27.805
[ALARM STOPS]

03:35.612 --> 03:38.916
[CLICKING]

03:38.916 --> 03:40.985
[BELL DINGS]

03:45.856 --> 03:47.725
[CLICKING]

03:47.725 --> 03:49.360
HI.

03:49.360 --> 03:51.729
UH, WHO GAVE YOU PERMISSION
TO BE BACK THERE?

03:51.729 --> 03:53.764
I DID.

03:53.764 --> 03:57.568
YOU KNOW, YOU SEEM TO BE
THE, UH, MANAGER HERE.

03:57.568 --> 03:59.536
THANK YOU.

03:59.536 --> 04:01.372
DO YOU HAVE
ANY WORKING COMPUTERS?

04:01.372 --> 04:02.272
NO, I'M AFRAID NOT, NO.

04:02.272 --> 04:03.407
HOW ABOUT A NEWSPAPER?

04:03.407 --> 04:05.576
THE <i>WAYWARD PINES CHRONICLE,</i>
YES.

04:05.576 --> 04:08.846
WE HAVEN'T HAD AN ISSUE
FOR ABOUT TWO WEEKS NOW.

04:08.846 --> 04:10.481
I GUESS THERE HASN'T BEEN
THAT MUCH NEWS.

04:10.481 --> 04:13.384
NO, I GUESS NOT.

04:13.384 --> 04:14.752
OH, SORRY, SIR, YOU'RE NOT
SUPPOSED TO -- MR. BURKE.

04:14.752 --> 04:16.420
[DOOR SLAMS]

04:16.420 --> 04:17.955
[CROW CAWS]

04:23.761 --> 04:24.995
[LOCK THUDS LIGHTLY]

04:34.905 --> 04:36.974
[CROW CAWS]

04:43.313 --> 04:44.715
[GLASS SHATTERS]

04:44.715 --> 04:46.884
[FLIES BUZZING]

04:53.357 --> 04:55.459
[GAGS]

05:11.475 --> 05:14.378
[BUZZING CONTINUES]

05:16.613 --> 05:18.582
[FLOORBOARD CREAKS]

05:18.582 --> 05:22.853
BREAKING AND ENTERING IS A MAJOR
FELONY IN THE GEM STATE.

05:22.853 --> 05:26.390
NOW, WHAT PART
OF "STAY IN YOUR HOTEL ROOM"

05:26.390 --> 05:28.025
DID YOU NOT UNDERSTAND?

05:28.025 --> 05:30.994
DIDN'T REALIZE
I WAS UNDER HOUSE ARREST.

05:30.994 --> 05:34.531
LOOK, THIS IS MY COLLEAGUE.

05:34.531 --> 05:37.668
I CAN'T JUST SIT BACK
AND NOT DO MY JOB.

05:37.668 --> 05:39.436
NOW, MAYBE YOU CAN'T
UNDERSTAND THAT,

05:39.436 --> 05:41.772
BEING A ONE-MAN OPERATION
AND ALL.

05:41.772 --> 05:45.676
[BUZZING CONTINUES]

05:45.676 --> 05:50.547
WHAT WERE YOU JUST DOING
WHEN I WALKED IN HERE?

05:50.547 --> 05:52.683
I SAW SOME MUD
AND SOME PINES NEEDLES

05:52.683 --> 05:54.351
ON THE BOTTOM
OF HIS BOOTS.

05:54.351 --> 05:56.520
HE MIGHT HAVE BEEN KILLED
IN THE WOODS

05:56.520 --> 05:58.288
AND BROUGHT HERE
AFTERWARDS.

05:58.288 --> 06:00.324
YEAH, THAT WAS ALREADY
IN MY REPORT.

06:00.324 --> 06:02.326
WHAT'S HIS BODY
STILL DOING HERE?

06:02.326 --> 06:03.861
WHERE'S FORENSICS?

06:03.861 --> 06:05.562
FORENSICS IS COMING
FROM BOISE,

06:05.562 --> 06:07.865
AND IT'S GONNA TAKE THEM
A COUPLE OF HOURS.

06:07.865 --> 06:09.967
I HOPE YOU HAVEN'T TAINTED
MY CRIME SCENE.

06:09.967 --> 06:12.436
NO, THE FLIES ALREADY
TOOK CARE OF THAT.

06:12.436 --> 06:14.805
MR. BURKE, I WANT YOU TO GO BACK
TO THE HOTEL ROOM.

06:14.805 --> 06:17.741
WE'LL LET THE PROFESSIONALS
DO THEIR JOB.

06:17.741 --> 06:19.476
FINE.

06:19.476 --> 06:21.512
I'M GONNA GO BACK
TO THE HOTEL.

06:23.347 --> 06:28.752
♪ <i>TIME AND TIME</i> ♪

06:28.752 --> 06:30.420
♪ <i>YEAH, HEY, HEY</i> ♪

06:30.420 --> 06:31.889
HEY.

06:31.889 --> 06:33.657
HEY.

06:33.657 --> 06:35.259
THANKS FOR THE CLOTHES.

06:35.259 --> 06:37.394
NO PROBLEM.
THEY LOOK CUTE.

06:37.394 --> 06:38.562
[CHUCKLES]

06:38.562 --> 06:40.297
THANKS.

06:40.297 --> 06:42.332
I WANT TO ASK YOU SOME MORE
QUESTIONS ABOUT BILL.

06:42.332 --> 06:44.468
DO YOU KNOW THIS SONG?

06:44.468 --> 06:46.503
OH, I LOVE THIS SONG.

06:46.503 --> 06:47.871
♪ <i>IT'S THE SAME THING,</i>
<i>SAME THING</i> ♪

06:47.871 --> 06:51.775
COME HERE AND DANCE WITH ME,
MR. BURKE.

06:51.775 --> 06:52.843
COME ON.

06:52.843 --> 06:55.779
[CHUCKLES]

06:55.779 --> 06:57.581
We have to talk
really quiet.

06:57.581 --> 07:00.918
There's mikes
under the barstools.

07:00.918 --> 07:03.554
YOU SAID
HE TRIED TO ESCAPE.

07:03.554 --> 07:06.490
I WAS SUPPOSED
TO ESCAPE WITH HIM.

07:06.490 --> 07:07.824
HOW WERE YOU GONNA DO THAT?

07:07.824 --> 07:10.794
HE HAD A PLAN.
HE HAD THIS NOTEBOOK.

07:10.794 --> 07:13.363
I FOUND IT.

07:13.363 --> 07:15.232
IT WAS STUCK IN HIS BOOT.

07:15.232 --> 07:17.668
WELL,
DON'T SHOW IT TO ME HERE.

07:17.668 --> 07:19.836
THERE'S CAMERAS
EVERYWHERE.

07:19.836 --> 07:23.574
THAT'S OKAY.
I DON'T HAVE IT.

07:23.574 --> 07:25.976
BUT I'LL GO GET IT.
[KNOCK ON GLASS]

07:25.976 --> 07:27.611
Man: HEY, BEVERLY.
I GET OFF AT 4:00.

07:27.611 --> 07:28.879
YOU CAN MEET ME
AT THE MAUSOLEUM,

07:28.879 --> 07:30.314
AND WE'LL TALK
ABOUT IT THEN.

07:30.314 --> 07:31.615
HERE.

07:31.615 --> 07:33.450
WHY DON'T YOU GET YOURSELF
COME COFFEE.

07:33.450 --> 07:35.752
THANKS.
OH, HEY, STAN.

07:35.752 --> 07:37.521
FINALLY.

07:37.521 --> 07:38.822
YOU KNOW, WE'VE OUT OF KETCHUP
FOR TWO DAYS.

07:38.822 --> 07:41.258
BYE, MR. BURKE!

07:43.293 --> 07:44.728
Theresa:
<i>YOU'VE REACHED THE BURKES.</i>

07:44.728 --> 07:46.330
<i>SORRY WE AREN'T HERE</i>
<i>TO TAKE YOUR CALL,</i>

07:46.330 --> 07:48.031
<i>UNLESS YOU'RE A TELEMARKETER,</i>

07:48.031 --> 07:49.800
<i>AND THEN WE ARE</i> THRILLED
<i>TO HAVE MISSED YOUR CALL.</i>

07:52.769 --> 07:55.439
[SIGHS]

07:55.439 --> 07:59.376
[Ringing]

07:59.376 --> 08:01.345
WOMAN:
Secret Service.

08:01.345 --> 08:03.447
YEAH, ETHAN BURKE
FOR ADAM HASSLER.

08:03.447 --> 08:04.948
He's not available
at the moment.

08:04.948 --> 08:06.917
Is there something
I can help you with?

08:06.917 --> 08:10.587
IS THIS MARCY?
Yes.

08:10.587 --> 08:13.757
MARCY, I LEFT A MESSAGE
THE OTHER DAY FOR ADAM HASSLER,

08:13.757 --> 08:15.025
AND I HAVEN'T HEARD
FROM HIM.

08:15.025 --> 08:16.827
If I said I would give him
the message,

08:16.827 --> 08:17.794
then I'm sure I did.

08:17.794 --> 08:19.463
OKAY.

08:19.463 --> 08:21.331
ARE YOU SITTING
AT THE RECEPTION DESK

08:21.331 --> 08:22.399
AT THE SEATTLE OFFICE?

08:22.399 --> 08:23.333
I have to go.

08:23.333 --> 08:24.501
IT'S A SIMPLE QUESTION.

08:24.501 --> 08:25.936
ARE YOU SITTING
AT THE SEVENTH-FLOOR

08:25.936 --> 08:27.871
RECEPTION DESK
AT THE SEATTLE OFFICE?

08:27.871 --> 08:29.539
Yes.
Now I really must go.

08:29.539 --> 08:31.775
THERE IS NO SEVENTH-FLOOR
RECEPTION DESK

08:31.775 --> 08:33.810
AT THE SEATTLE OFFICE.
WHO ARE YOU?

08:33.810 --> 08:35.345
[Click, dial tone]

08:36.947 --> 08:39.516
ALL SET, MR. BURKE.

08:51.862 --> 08:55.365
YOU GIVE THAT TO ME.
YEAH.

08:55.365 --> 08:56.600
AND I GIVE THIS TO YOU.

08:56.600 --> 08:59.569
THANKS.

08:59.569 --> 09:02.539
YOU MUST KNOW JUST ABOUT
EVERYBODY IN THIS TOWN.

09:02.539 --> 09:05.242
AND ALMOST EVERYTHING
ABOUT THEM.

09:07.311 --> 09:10.580
DO YOU KNOW WHERE
I MIGHT FIND KATE HEWSON?

09:10.580 --> 09:12.649
KATE HEWSON --
I DON'T KNOW HER.

09:12.649 --> 09:14.484
HOW CAN THAT BE POSSIBLE?

09:16.753 --> 09:18.021
AH.

09:18.021 --> 09:19.523
BALLINGER.

09:19.523 --> 09:21.525
OH. YEAH.
SHE'S SUPER NICE.

09:21.525 --> 09:24.027
SHE'S BEEN COMING IN HERE
FOR YEARS.

09:24.027 --> 09:25.896
SHE WORKS AT THE TOY STORE.

09:25.896 --> 09:29.366
THANKS.
MM-HMM.

09:32.969 --> 09:35.339
HEY.
HI.

09:35.339 --> 09:36.673
SORRY I'M LATE.

09:36.673 --> 09:38.508
8:30 IS LATE, ETHAN.

09:38.508 --> 09:39.776
IT'S MIDNIGHT.

09:39.776 --> 09:41.411
HUH?

09:41.411 --> 09:43.613
OH, YEAH, I SHOULD HAVE CALLED.
[SIGHS]

09:43.613 --> 09:45.549
THINGS GOT A LITTLE
COMPLICATED AT WORK.

09:45.549 --> 09:46.983
REALLY?

09:46.983 --> 09:49.853
ANYBODY <i>I</i> KNOW?

09:49.853 --> 09:52.022
THERESA, IT'S OVER.

09:52.022 --> 09:54.558
COME HERE.

09:56.693 --> 09:58.428
I LOVE YOU.

10:00.397 --> 10:01.965
OKAY, GET A ROOM.

10:01.965 --> 10:03.500
GET A ROOM?

10:03.500 --> 10:05.736
LAST TIME WE GOT A ROOM,
WE ENDED UP WITH YOU.

10:05.736 --> 10:08.438
Man: <i>STILL NO CLUES IN THE</i>
<i>QUEEN ANNE DISTRICT ASSAULTS.</i>

10:08.438 --> 10:10.240
WHY ISN'T IT ON THE NEWS?

10:10.240 --> 10:11.508
[RADIO SHUTS OFF]

10:11.508 --> 10:13.944
BECAUSE IT'S
CLASSIFIED WHILE --

10:13.944 --> 10:16.613
WHILE THEY INVESTIGATE,
SWEETIE.

10:16.613 --> 10:18.582
WHAT ISN'T CLASSIFIED
WHEN IT COMES TO DAD?

10:18.582 --> 10:19.950
IT'S HIS EXCUSE
FOR EVERYTHING.

10:19.950 --> 10:22.419
WHAT IF HE'S DEAD?
HE'S NOT DEAD.

10:22.419 --> 10:25.322
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?
IT'S BEEN FIVE DAYS.

10:25.322 --> 10:28.458
UNLESS HE'S WITH
THAT WOMAN AGAIN.

10:31.461 --> 10:32.529
WHICH WOULD BE WORSE?

10:34.498 --> 10:37.401
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

10:47.911 --> 10:49.780
[GIGGLES]

10:51.481 --> 10:53.583
[INDISTINCT WHISPERING]

11:04.861 --> 11:05.962
[DOOR BELL JINGLES]

11:11.835 --> 11:13.870
TO WHAT DO I OWE
THE PLEASURE?

11:13.870 --> 11:16.940
I JUST THOUGHT I'D STOP BY
AND SAY "HI."

11:16.940 --> 11:18.975
THAT WAS SO NICE OF YOU.

11:18.975 --> 11:20.677
HOW ARE YOU TODAY?

11:20.677 --> 11:23.313
I'M GREAT, I THINK.

11:23.313 --> 11:26.349
I HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE TO GET AHOLD
OF ANYBODY SINCE I GOT HERE,

11:26.349 --> 11:27.551
AND I CAN'T LEAVE.

11:27.551 --> 11:29.986
AND THE ONLY REASON
THAT I'M HERE

11:29.986 --> 11:31.955
IS BECAUSE I WAS SENT HERE

11:31.955 --> 11:34.691
TO FIND YOU AND BILL EVANS.

11:34.691 --> 11:37.727
AND GUESS WHAT?
I FOUND BOTH OF YOU.

11:37.727 --> 11:42.766
ONLY YOU'RE...WORKING
IN A TOY STORE

11:42.766 --> 11:45.235
AND LIVING IN A HOUSE
WITH A PICKET FENCE

11:45.235 --> 11:46.503
AND A MAN NAMED HAROLD,

11:46.503 --> 11:48.505
AND BILL EVANS'
MUTILATED CORPSE

11:48.505 --> 11:52.476
IS ROTTING IN AN ABANDONED HOUSE
ON THE OUTSKIRTS OF TOWN,

11:52.476 --> 11:56.313
WHICH I FOUND
A LITTLE BIT SURPRISING.

11:56.313 --> 12:00.317
BUT OTHER THAN THAT,
I COULDN'T BE HAPPIER.

12:00.317 --> 12:02.786
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM, KATE?

12:02.786 --> 12:06.690
AND WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

12:06.690 --> 12:08.358
EVERYTHING OKAY OUT HERE?

12:08.358 --> 12:10.660
OH, WE'RE FINE, HAROLD.
THANK YOU. [CHUCKLES]

12:10.660 --> 12:13.029
ETHAN, I DON'T THINK YOU'VE
FORMALLY MET MY HUSBAND.

12:13.029 --> 12:15.832
NO, NOT FORMALLY.

12:15.832 --> 12:17.734
NICE TO MEET YOU FORMALLY.
[CHUCKLES]

12:17.734 --> 12:19.402
WELL, I'M A LITTLE
UNDER THE GUN.

12:19.402 --> 12:20.871
I'M FILLING AN ORDER
FOR THE SCHOOL,

12:20.871 --> 12:22.572
SO I SHOULD GET BACK
TO THAT, BUT...

12:22.572 --> 12:24.574
LET'S GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER
BETTER REAL SOON.

12:24.574 --> 12:26.309
I LOOK FORWARD TO IT.

12:26.309 --> 12:27.410
GREAT.

12:31.848 --> 12:34.384
WOW. I NEVER GOT
THE WEDDING INVITATION.

12:34.384 --> 12:35.952
WE KEPT IT INTIMATE.

12:35.952 --> 12:38.455
YEAH, SO DID WE.

12:38.455 --> 12:41.591
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
I CAN HELP YOU WITH?

12:41.591 --> 12:42.559
YEAH, HERE.

12:43.393 --> 12:45.362
RING UP THIS.

12:46.263 --> 12:47.464
ETHAN.

12:47.464 --> 12:48.965
RING UP THE DUCKS.

12:48.965 --> 12:50.333
[CLEARS THROAT]

12:52.269 --> 12:54.237
WHAT WRONG WITH THIS MONEY,
KATE?

12:54.237 --> 12:59.409
THE DATE ON EVERY BILL
IS 1988 OR EARLIER.

12:59.409 --> 13:01.478
THE TREASURY SEAL,
IT'S COUNTERFEIT.

13:01.478 --> 13:04.281
ANY TRAINED AGENT
COULD SEE THAT.

13:04.281 --> 13:06.449
THIS WHOLE TOWN IS FLOODED
WITH COUNTERFEIT MONEY.

13:06.449 --> 13:07.851
IT'S FAKE!

13:09.719 --> 13:12.556
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING?

13:12.556 --> 13:15.659
WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO WRAP THIS UP?

13:15.659 --> 13:17.460
NO.

13:17.460 --> 13:18.995
I WANT YOU TO ANSWER ME.

13:18.995 --> 13:20.564
WHAT HAPPENED TO EVANS?

13:20.564 --> 13:23.333
IT REALLY IS SO SAD
ABOUT BILL EVANS,

13:23.333 --> 13:24.935
ESPECIALLY FOR HIS WIDOW.

13:24.935 --> 13:26.870
HE WASN'T MARRIED.
YOU KNOW THAT.

13:26.870 --> 13:28.872
PATRICIA.

13:28.872 --> 13:30.941
I DON'T THINK SHE'S LEFT
THE HOUSE SINCE HE DIED.

13:30.941 --> 13:33.610
I USED TO SEE HER
EVERY MORNING,

13:33.610 --> 13:35.645
WATERING HER PINK HYDRANGEAS

13:35.645 --> 13:38.548
IN FRONT OF
THEIR LIGHT BROWN HOUSE.

13:41.451 --> 13:42.752
[CHUCKLES]

13:42.752 --> 13:44.854
PATRICIA HAS A REAL WAY
WITH FLOWERS.

13:55.498 --> 13:57.601
"DO NOT TRY TO LEAVE.

13:57.601 --> 13:59.736
"DO NOT DISCUSS THE PAST.

13:59.736 --> 14:04.307
"DO NOT DISCUSS
YOUR LIFE BEFORE.

14:04.307 --> 14:08.511
ALWAYS ANSWER THE PHONE
IF IT RINGS."

14:08.511 --> 14:11.948
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

14:11.948 --> 14:15.352
BALLINGER TOYS.

14:16.553 --> 14:18.688
[DOOR BELL JINGLES]

14:40.979 --> 14:42.147
HI.

14:42.147 --> 14:43.281
CAN I HELP YOU?

14:43.281 --> 14:45.016
ARE YOU MRS. WILLIAM EVANS?

14:45.016 --> 14:47.118
YES, I AM.

14:47.118 --> 14:49.721
YOU ARE?

14:49.721 --> 14:50.922
MY NAME IS ETHAN BURKE.

14:50.922 --> 14:52.223
BILL AND I WERE COLLEAGUES.

14:52.223 --> 14:54.626
WE WORKED TOGETHER
AT THE SECRET SERVICE.

14:54.626 --> 14:57.028
I'M VERY SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

14:57.028 --> 15:00.598
OH, BILL DIDN'T WORK
FOR THE SECRET SERVICE.

15:00.598 --> 15:01.866
HE MOWED LAWNS.

15:04.235 --> 15:06.905
DO YOU MIND ME ASKING
HOW LONG

15:06.905 --> 15:08.974
YOU AND BILL WERE MARRIED?

15:08.974 --> 15:10.875
ALMOST A YEAR.

15:10.875 --> 15:13.244
[BABY CRYING]
WELL, I DON'T MEAN
TO ALARM YOU, MRS. EVANS,

15:13.244 --> 15:15.547
BUT THERE'S NO RECORD OF BILL
EVER HAVING BEEN MARRIED.

15:15.547 --> 15:17.782
LOOK, I'M ALONE
WITH A NEWBORN BABY,

15:17.782 --> 15:19.117
SO IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME.

15:19.117 --> 15:23.121
I WAS SENT HERE
TO FIND THIS MAN.

15:23.121 --> 15:26.958
NOW, I HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE
THAT HE WAS MURDERED.

15:26.958 --> 15:30.729
MY HUSBAND WASN'T MURDERED.

15:30.729 --> 15:32.831
HE KILLED HIMSELF.

15:32.831 --> 15:35.333
ARE YOU SURE?

15:35.333 --> 15:37.135
[Voice breaking]
AM I SURE?

15:37.135 --> 15:39.070
I WATCHED IT.

15:40.138 --> 15:44.676
♪ <i>THIS TOWN IS GETTING OLD</i> ♪

15:44.676 --> 15:47.212
IS POPE BACK THERE?

15:47.212 --> 15:50.248
♪ <i>THE WHISTLE BLOWS...</i> ♪

15:50.248 --> 15:52.717
MAY I HELP YOU?

15:52.717 --> 15:55.553
WE'RE NOT GONNA DO THIS AGAIN,
ARE WE?

15:55.553 --> 15:57.255
COME ON, YOU KNOW WHO I AM.

15:57.255 --> 15:58.990
YES, WE ALL KNOW WHO YOU ARE,
MR. BURKE,

15:58.990 --> 16:00.992
AND WE'RE ALL VERY IMPRESSED
BY YOUR CREDENTIALS.

16:00.992 --> 16:03.995
WELL, WHERE'S POPE?
I DON'T KNOW.

16:03.995 --> 16:08.133
LET ME LOOK IN MY MAGIC 8 BALL
AND FIND OUT.

16:08.133 --> 16:10.668
OH, WAIT A MINUTE,
I DON'T HAVE A MAGIC 8 BALL.

16:10.668 --> 16:11.970
WHY DON'T YOU HAVE A SEAT?

16:11.970 --> 16:14.272
FIND ANY SUSPECTS,
MR. BURKE?

16:16.641 --> 16:18.076
BECAUSE I FOUND ONE.

16:18.076 --> 16:19.911
THIS ICE CREAM CONE HERE?

16:19.911 --> 16:23.014
IT'S BEEN UP TO NO GOOD.

16:24.983 --> 16:27.852
LIKE SOMEBODY ELSE
IN THIS ROOM.

16:27.852 --> 16:30.555
YOU KNOW, MR. BURKE,

16:30.555 --> 16:32.891
I'M STARTING TO GET
THE DISTINCT IMPRESSION

16:32.891 --> 16:35.627
THAT YOU'RE NOT SO HAPPY
WITH YOUR ACCOMMODATIONS.

16:35.627 --> 16:37.629
PERHAPS I SHOULD UPGRADE YOU
TO A SUITE

16:37.629 --> 16:40.799
OR ONE OF THESE CELLS.
[Chuckling]COME ON.

16:40.799 --> 16:42.167
YOU DON'T EXPECT ME TO STAY

16:42.167 --> 16:44.069
IN THAT HOTEL ROOM ALL DAY,
DO YOU?

16:44.069 --> 16:46.171
YOU HAVEN'T SPENT ANY TIME
IN THERE AT ALL.

16:49.207 --> 16:53.878
I HEAR YOU PAID PATRICIA EVANS
A VISIT.

16:53.878 --> 16:57.082
HERE THE POOR WOMAN IS GRIEVING
OVER HER DEAD HUSBAND,

16:57.082 --> 17:01.219
AND YOU GO BANGING ON HER DOOR
LIKE A DRUNKEN BIBLE SALESMAN.

17:01.219 --> 17:03.855
I DIDN'T KNOW EVANS WAS MARRIED
WITH A BABY.

17:03.855 --> 17:06.858
YOU THINK THE BABY DID IT,
HUH?

17:08.760 --> 17:10.295
ANY WORD FROM FORENSICS?

17:10.295 --> 17:13.765
THEY PICKED UP YOUR FRIEND'S
BODY ABOUT AN HOUR AGO.

17:13.765 --> 17:16.301
THEY SAID THEY SHOULD HAVE
RESULTS BACK

17:16.301 --> 17:17.769
BY TOMORROW MORNING.

17:17.769 --> 17:20.004
HIS WIFE SAYS
HE KILLED HIMSELF.

17:21.539 --> 17:27.779
NOW, MR. BURKE,
I KNOW THAT YOU THINK

17:27.779 --> 17:31.583
THAT NOTHING SEEMS TO MAKE SENSE
IN THIS TOWN,

17:31.583 --> 17:35.553
BUT ONE VERY IMPORTANT DETAIL
YOU HAVEN'T MENTIONED

17:35.553 --> 17:40.125
IS THAT YOU WERE IN A BIG-TIME
ACCIDENT WITH A VERY LARGE SEMI,

17:40.125 --> 17:42.760
THE DOCTORS FOUND BLEEDING
ON YOUR BRAIN,

17:42.760 --> 17:45.964
THEY WANTED TO DRAIN THE BLOOD,
BUT YOU FLED THE HOSPITAL.

17:45.964 --> 17:47.198
AM I RIGHT?

17:51.836 --> 17:53.938
IS THE BODY
IN THE MORGUE YET?

17:53.938 --> 17:55.840
SURE IS.

17:55.840 --> 17:57.909
IN THE HOSPITAL.

17:57.909 --> 17:59.844
GOOD.

17:59.844 --> 18:01.613
WELL, I-I'D LIKE
TO GO OVER THERE NOW.

18:01.613 --> 18:02.947
DON'T.

18:02.947 --> 18:05.717
I WANT YOU TO STAY AWAY
FROM THE BODY.

18:05.717 --> 18:07.886
LEAVE IT
TO THE PROFESSIONALS.

18:07.886 --> 18:10.889
OKAY.

18:16.127 --> 18:18.930
LET ME KNOW
WHAT THE CORONER SAYS.

18:25.136 --> 18:27.071
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

19:21.159 --> 19:22.894
[PAPER RUSTLES]

19:37.909 --> 19:40.011
MR. BURKE.

19:42.680 --> 19:45.016
CAN'T SEEM TO STAY AWAY
FROM THIS PLACE, CAN YOU?

19:45.016 --> 19:47.952
IS THE CORONER AROUND?

19:47.952 --> 19:51.623
NO, HE LEFT.
MAYBE I CAN HELP YOU, HMM?

19:54.926 --> 19:57.862
I THOUGHT
YOU WORKED UPSTAIRS.

19:57.862 --> 19:59.864
I GO WHERE I'M NEEDED.

19:59.864 --> 20:02.133
DO YOU NEED ME, MR. BURKE?

20:02.133 --> 20:03.868
NO.

20:03.868 --> 20:06.604
WERE YOU ABLE
TO REACH YOUR WIFE?

20:06.604 --> 20:08.873
I KNOW YOU REALLY WANTED
TO TALK TO HER.

20:11.042 --> 20:13.111
BET WHEN YOU TWO
GET BACK TOGETHER,

20:13.111 --> 20:15.280
YOU'RE GONNA BANG HER BRAINS
OUT, HUH?

20:37.902 --> 20:40.672
BEN, THERESA!

21:03.261 --> 21:05.964
Dr. Jenkins: MR. BURKE.

21:05.964 --> 21:07.599
THANK HEAVEN YOU'RE BACK.

21:07.599 --> 21:09.334
WHERE ARE THEY?

21:11.370 --> 21:13.305
WHO?

21:13.305 --> 21:15.173
MY WIFE!

21:15.173 --> 21:18.276
MY -- MY WIFE AND MY SON.

21:18.276 --> 21:20.612
I JUST SAW THEM...

21:20.612 --> 21:24.883
COMING DOWN THIS --
THEY WERE --

21:24.883 --> 21:27.052
THEY WERE ON, UH, STRETCHERS
COMING DOWN THIS HALLWAY.

21:27.052 --> 21:31.223
MR. BURKE, NO NEW PATIENTS HAVE
BEEN ADMITTED SINCE YOU LEFT.

21:31.223 --> 21:33.191
YOU SHOULD COME
AND LIE DOWN.

21:33.191 --> 21:35.861
NO, NO, NO.
I'M FINE.

21:35.861 --> 21:38.897
WE LOST TRACK OF YOU
THE OTHER NIGHT

21:38.897 --> 21:43.101
BEFORE I HAD A CHANCE TO TREAT
YOUR BRAIN HEMORRHAGE.

21:43.101 --> 21:45.170
WE'VE BEEN VERY CONCERNED.

21:45.170 --> 21:47.906
I JUST SAW THEM!

21:47.906 --> 21:49.841
I'M NOT SAYING YOU DIDN'T.

21:54.479 --> 21:57.249
YOU MISS THEM A LOT,
DON'T YOU?

21:59.918 --> 22:03.221
I'D LIKE TO SEE
MY...MY CHART.

22:03.221 --> 22:06.124
BY ALL MEANS.
I'LL FIND YOUR CHART.
PLEASE DO THAT.

22:06.124 --> 22:07.959
BUT PLEASE, WON'T YOU SIT DOWN
JUST FOR A MOMENT?

22:12.898 --> 22:15.500
[SIGHS]

22:15.500 --> 22:17.369
MR. BURKE...

22:17.369 --> 22:21.239
EVERY SECOND,
YOUR CONDITION IS WORSENING.

22:21.239 --> 22:24.276
UNLESS I CAN GET YOU
INTO SURGERY,

22:24.276 --> 22:30.515
THESE HALLUCINATIONS WILL --
WILL BECOME MORE FREQUENT

22:30.515 --> 22:33.518
AND MORE INTENSE.

22:33.518 --> 22:37.289
HAVE YOU NOTICED ANYTHING ELSE
GO UNEXPLAINED?

22:41.993 --> 22:44.996
I WANT TO HELP YOU,
MR. BURKE.

22:44.996 --> 22:48.300
BUT YOU HAVE TO GIVE ME
YOUR CONSENT.

22:48.300 --> 22:51.870
DO I HAVE YOUR CONSENT,

22:51.870 --> 22:53.371
MR. BURKE?

22:55.006 --> 22:58.076
NURSE, WOULD YOU GET HIS CHARTS,
AND THEN WE CAN GET STARTED?

22:58.076 --> 23:00.312
Nurse Pam:
OF COURSE, DOCTOR.

23:00.312 --> 23:01.313
RIGHT AWAY.

23:01.313 --> 23:03.482
THANK YOU, NURSE.

23:12.624 --> 23:14.326
YOU KNOW WE CAN'T
BREAK PROTOCOL.

23:14.326 --> 23:15.894
IF HIS FACE WAS ON TV,

23:15.894 --> 23:17.362
WE COULD GET LEADS OR TIPS
OR SOMETHING.

23:17.362 --> 23:19.264
WE ARE DOING EVERYTHING
THAT WE CAN.

23:19.264 --> 23:21.633
EXCEPT ANYTHING THAT COULD
EMBARRASS THE AGENCY,

23:21.633 --> 23:23.101
AND IN THE MEANTIME,

23:23.101 --> 23:24.970
HE COULD DIE
IF HE ISN'T DEAD ALREADY.

23:24.970 --> 23:26.538
I AM AS FRUSTRATED
AS YOU ARE.

23:26.538 --> 23:27.939
THEN ACT LIKE IT!

23:30.041 --> 23:32.043
I'M SORRY, ADAM.

23:32.043 --> 23:33.879
HOW'S BEN HOLDING UP?

23:33.879 --> 23:37.883
HE THINKS HIS FATHER RAN OFF
WITH KATE HEWSON.

23:37.883 --> 23:39.985
NO.

23:39.985 --> 23:41.419
HE WOULD NOT DO THAT.

23:41.419 --> 23:42.888
Not after --

23:42.888 --> 23:45.023
HE TRANSFERRED TO BOISE,
RIGHT?

23:45.023 --> 23:49.127
THERESA, I CAN'T --

23:49.127 --> 23:51.563
YOU CAN'T DISCLOSE ANY DETAILS.
I KNOW, I KNOW.

23:51.563 --> 23:53.932
I HEARD IT A MILLION TIMES
FROM ETHAN

23:53.932 --> 23:55.967
TO THE POINT
WHERE WE BARELY TALKED.

23:55.967 --> 23:57.202
THERESA.

23:57.202 --> 23:59.271
I need to know if Ethan
is in Boise.

24:01.907 --> 24:03.308
[SIGHS]

24:09.281 --> 24:11.316
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU WENT TO THE HOSPITAL.

24:11.316 --> 24:13.318
MAYBE YOU DO HAVE
BRAIN DAMAGE.

24:13.318 --> 24:15.520
I THOUGHT
I SAW MY WIFE AND KID.

24:15.520 --> 24:17.522
MAYBE YOU DID.

24:17.522 --> 24:21.159
GET THIS.

24:24.229 --> 24:27.165
IT'S SOME KIND OF...

24:27.165 --> 24:28.567
ESCAPE PLAN.

24:28.567 --> 24:30.869
MAYBE WE CAN USE IT.

24:30.869 --> 24:32.938
WELL,
BEFORE WE DO ANYTHING,

24:32.938 --> 24:35.607
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO TAKE OUT
YOUR MICROCHIP.

24:35.607 --> 24:37.142
MY WHAT?

24:39.611 --> 24:42.581
[GROANS]

24:42.581 --> 24:44.482
AAH!
SORRY.

24:44.482 --> 24:47.152
I DON'T HAVE ANY ACTUAL
MEDICAL TRAINING.

24:47.152 --> 24:50.322
NO KIDDING.
LET ME GET IT.

24:50.322 --> 24:52.591
[GROANS]

24:57.495 --> 24:59.431
CAN'T THEY TRACK US
IN HERE?

24:59.431 --> 25:02.133
I'VE HIDDEN IN HERE BEFORE
WITH THE CHIP.

25:02.133 --> 25:05.070
I THINK THE THICK STONE WALLS
DISRUPT THE SIGNAL.

25:05.070 --> 25:08.006
[WINCES]

25:08.006 --> 25:09.341
OW.

25:09.341 --> 25:10.508
I GOT IT.

25:10.508 --> 25:12.244
I GOT IT, I GOT IT.

25:12.244 --> 25:14.246
OKAY,
NOW PUT IT IN YOUR POCKET

25:14.246 --> 25:16.348
SO THEY DON'T KNOW
YOU REMOVED IT.

25:16.348 --> 25:18.250
YOU'LL DITCH IT
AS SOON AS WE RUN.

25:18.250 --> 25:21.486
THIS IS THE SAME TECHNOLOGY
THEY USE TO TRACK ANIMALS.

25:21.486 --> 25:24.256
YOU GOT ANYTHING
TO CLOSE THIS WOUND?

25:24.256 --> 25:25.991
JUST DUCT TAPE.

25:25.991 --> 25:27.459
IT'S BETTER THAN NOTHING.
HMM.

25:27.459 --> 25:29.928
[DUCT TAPE RIPS]

25:29.928 --> 25:32.998
ALL RIGHT.

25:32.998 --> 25:36.534
[SIGHS]
SO, WHAT'S OUR PLAN?

25:36.534 --> 25:40.071
"OUR" PLAN?
YOU'RE THE SECRET SERVICE AGENT.

25:40.071 --> 25:42.173
YOU'RE GONNA COME UP
WITH A PLAN.

25:42.173 --> 25:45.176
IF I COULD COME UP WITH A PLAN,
I WOULD HAVE LEFT A YEAR AGO.

25:45.176 --> 25:48.847
DID YOU TELL ME THAT
YOU CAME HERE IN 1999,

25:48.847 --> 25:50.515
OR AM I HALLUCINATING?

25:50.515 --> 25:52.384
YOU WEREN'T HALLUCINATING.

25:52.384 --> 25:55.020
AND THAT WAS A YEAR AGO?

25:55.020 --> 25:56.588
MM-HMM.

25:56.588 --> 26:01.393
WELL, I CAME HERE FIVE DAYS AGO,
AND IT WAS 2014.

26:03.328 --> 26:04.896
WHO WAS YOUR PRESIDENT?

26:04.896 --> 26:07.866
BILL CLINTON.

26:07.866 --> 26:10.235
YOU EVER HEARD OF OBAMA?

26:10.235 --> 26:11.369
9/11?

26:14.973 --> 26:16.975
WHEN'S YOUR BIRTHDAY?

26:16.975 --> 26:18.610
NOVEMBER 1st.

26:18.610 --> 26:20.278
WHAT YEAR?

26:20.278 --> 26:21.613
1960.

26:21.613 --> 26:23.548
HUH.

26:23.548 --> 26:25.850
YOU LOOK PRETTY GOOD
FOR 54.

26:29.154 --> 26:32.624
WELL, I GUESS THAT'S A POINT
IN THE "PLUS" COLUMN.

26:35.060 --> 26:36.995
LOOK AT THESE TOMBSTONES.

26:36.995 --> 26:38.964
THERE'S NO NAMES, DATES.

26:38.964 --> 26:40.565
THE MORE YOU SEE,

26:40.565 --> 26:44.569
THE LESS ANYTHING MAKES SENSE
IN THIS TOWN.

26:44.569 --> 26:46.838
WHEN I FIRST WOKE UP HERE,

26:46.838 --> 26:48.606
I WAS SO DISORIENTED
THAT I BELIEVED THEM

26:48.606 --> 26:50.508
WHEN THEY TOLD ME
I LIVED HERE.

26:50.508 --> 26:54.612
I REMEMBER WALKING AROUND
IN THIS FOG

26:54.612 --> 26:58.149
WITH NO COMPETING MEMORIES.

26:58.149 --> 27:00.118
EVENTUALLY, THEY CAME BACK,

27:00.118 --> 27:02.854
AND NOW I JUST
KEEP MY HEAD DOWN,

27:02.854 --> 27:04.556
I GO TO WORK, I GO HOME.

27:04.556 --> 27:07.058
AND I KNOW
THIS ISN'T MY LIFE.

27:07.058 --> 27:09.594
DIDN'T TAKE ME TOO LONG
TO REALIZE

27:09.594 --> 27:13.565
THAT IT WAS THE FEAR THAT KEEPS
EVERYBODY IN LINE HERE.

27:13.565 --> 27:16.601
FEAR OF WHAT?

27:16.601 --> 27:19.104
WHAT HAPPENED
TO BILL EVANS.

27:19.104 --> 27:21.940
WHO KILLED HIM?

27:23.975 --> 27:26.011
SHERIFF POPE.

27:27.512 --> 27:30.281
HE CUT HIS THROAT
WHILE THE WHOLE TOWN WATCHED.

27:38.132 --> 27:40.468
BILL AND I HAD A TIME
AND A PLACE

27:40.468 --> 27:42.203
ALL FIGURED OUT
AND EVERYTHING,

27:42.203 --> 27:44.539
AND THEN TWO DAYS BEFORE...
[DOOR CLOSES]

27:44.539 --> 27:46.607
I THINK HE JUST SNAPPED.

27:46.607 --> 27:51.379
AND HE TOOK OFF ALL BY HIMSELF,
AND HE GAVE ME NO WARNING.

27:51.379 --> 27:53.481
WELL, YOU'RE ALIVE
BECAUSE OF IT.

27:53.481 --> 27:55.149
YEAH, I'D RATHER DIE

27:55.149 --> 27:56.551
THAN PRETEND THIS IS NORMAL
FOR ONE MORE DAY.

27:58.252 --> 28:00.321
HEY.

28:00.321 --> 28:02.557
HOLD THIS.

28:02.557 --> 28:05.693
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

28:19.140 --> 28:22.210
THE CAMERAS PING OFF
THE MOVEMENT OF THE CHIP.

28:22.210 --> 28:23.978
OH.

28:23.978 --> 28:25.646
THERE'S HARDLY ANY CARS
AROUND HERE.

28:25.646 --> 28:28.516
YEAH, CARS.
[CHUCKLES]

28:28.516 --> 28:31.986
I HAVEN'T SEEN A SINGLE AIRPLANE
THE WHOLE TIME I'VE BEEN HERE.

28:31.986 --> 28:35.022
NOW, LOOK WHO IT IS.
[CHUCKLES]

28:35.022 --> 28:37.191
KATE!
KATE.

28:37.191 --> 28:39.193
HI...HAROLD.

28:39.193 --> 28:41.729
UM, ETHAN, THIS IS KATE
AND HAROLD BALLINGER.

28:41.729 --> 28:44.065
WE KNOW EACH OTHER.

28:44.065 --> 28:47.702
I'M SO GLAD YOU TWO ARE --
IS THIS A DATE?

28:47.702 --> 28:49.203
[CHUCKLES]

28:49.203 --> 28:51.472
WELL, I'M --
NO.

28:51.472 --> 28:53.374
I-I-I MEAN, WELL --

28:53.374 --> 28:55.309
IT'S NOT --
I HAVE AN IDEA.

28:55.309 --> 28:57.645
WHY DON'T THE TWO OF YOU COME
OVER FOR DINNER TOMORROW NIGHT?

28:57.645 --> 28:59.013
WE SHOULD GET TO KNOW
BOTH OF YOU BETTER.

28:59.013 --> 29:00.248
THAT WOULD BE PERFECT.

29:00.248 --> 29:03.384
OH, GREAT.
THAT -- THAT WOULD BE GREAT.

29:03.384 --> 29:05.519
WE'D LOVE THAT.

29:05.519 --> 29:08.022
EXCELLENT.
WE LOOK FORWARD TO IT.

29:08.022 --> 29:09.090
LET'S SAY 7:30?

29:09.090 --> 29:10.358
7:30?

29:10.358 --> 29:12.059
OKAY.
YEAH.

29:12.059 --> 29:14.295
SEE YOU THEN.

29:16.130 --> 29:19.600
ARE WE REALLY
GOING TO DINNER?

29:19.600 --> 29:20.635
YES, WE ARE.

29:20.635 --> 29:23.704
TRUST ME.

29:26.574 --> 29:28.676
Man: <i>LIGHT RAIN</i>
<i>FOR THE NEXT THREE DAYS</i>

29:28.676 --> 29:30.611
<i>IN MUCH OF</i>
<i>THE PACIFIC NORTHWEST,</i>

29:30.611 --> 29:32.513
<i>BUT BY THURSDAY,</i>

29:32.513 --> 29:34.482
<i>WE'RE LOOKING AT A WEEK-LONG</i>
<i>STREAK OF SUNSHINE AND --</i>

29:34.482 --> 29:36.751
Theresa:
I'M GOING TO BOISE.

29:36.751 --> 29:39.053
WHAT?

29:39.053 --> 29:40.988
YEAH,
I'M GONNA FIND HIM MYSELF.

29:40.988 --> 29:42.189
NOW?

29:42.189 --> 29:44.025
NO, IN THE MORNING.

29:46.060 --> 29:50.531
EITHER ETHAN IS DEAD OR
HE HAS ABANDONED HIS FAMILY,

29:50.531 --> 29:54.201
AND I'M GONNA FIND OUT
WHICH ONE IT IS.

29:54.201 --> 29:56.370
AND IF IT IS THE LATTER,

29:56.370 --> 29:58.739
THEN I AM GOING
TO KILL HIM MYSELF.

29:58.739 --> 30:01.175
OH, CAN I HELP?

30:01.175 --> 30:03.678
YES,
YOU CAN STAY WITH BEN.

30:03.678 --> 30:05.313
I'M COMING WITH YOU.

30:05.313 --> 30:08.182
NO, SWEETIE, YOU HAVE TO
STAY WITH AUNT DARLA.

30:08.182 --> 30:09.250
YOU HAVE SCHOOL.

30:09.250 --> 30:12.386
NO, I'M COMING WITH YOU.

30:14.388 --> 30:16.090
[CHUCKLES LIGHTLY]

31:09.276 --> 31:11.612
AND VERY DEMANDING.
MM-HMM.

31:11.612 --> 31:14.181
HE'S BARGING IN,
SAYING "WHERE'S SHERIFF POPE?

31:14.181 --> 31:16.650
I'M A SECRET-SERVICE AGENT.
I GOT A BIG EMERGENCY."

31:16.650 --> 31:18.519
IT'S DRIVING ARNIE CRAZY.

31:18.519 --> 31:21.489
WELL, HE'S A WILD ONE,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

31:21.489 --> 31:23.090
THANK YOU.

31:23.090 --> 31:26.093
SLAMMED ME INTO A WALL
JUST A FEW DAYS AGO.

31:26.093 --> 31:29.230
YOU EVER TRY AND SUTURE
YOUR OWN NOSE, ARLENE?

31:29.230 --> 31:32.433
I HEARD HE'S BEEN HERE
QUITE A BIT.

31:32.433 --> 31:34.668
[SCOFFS]

31:34.668 --> 31:36.537
HE'S PROBABLY GOT A LITTLE THING
FOR YOU, BEVERLY.

31:36.537 --> 31:38.038
WOULDN'T THAT BE NICE,
BEVERLY?

31:38.038 --> 31:40.541
FINALLY SETTLE DOWN
WITH SOMEONE, HMM?

31:40.541 --> 31:42.410
I DON'T THINK SO, OKAY?

31:42.410 --> 31:45.980
HE HAS A WIFE,
AND HE MISSES HIS WIFE A LOT.

31:45.980 --> 31:47.548
OH, SO YOU TALK TO HIM.

31:47.548 --> 31:49.250
WELL, IT'S MY JOB,

31:49.250 --> 31:52.019
IF SOMEBODY'S GONNA SIT THERE,
THAT I TALK TO THEM.

31:52.019 --> 31:56.157
BUT NOT ABOUT THE PAST.

31:56.157 --> 31:58.692
NEVER.

31:58.692 --> 32:01.195
♪ <i>...IN THE SHADOWS</i>
<i>BY THE STREET LIGHT</i> ♪

32:01.195 --> 32:02.363
♪ <i>ON THE SIDEWALK...</i> ♪

32:05.366 --> 32:07.401
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

32:56.450 --> 32:57.985
[GUNSHOT]

32:57.985 --> 33:00.988
[WINGS FLUTTER]

33:00.988 --> 33:03.991
[GUNSHOT]

33:07.461 --> 33:09.430
[GUNSHOT]

33:27.478 --> 33:29.680
NICE HOUSE YOU GOT HERE.

33:29.680 --> 33:34.752
I HOPE I NEVER SEE
THIS HOUSE AGAIN.

33:34.752 --> 33:37.288
MAYBE WE SHOULDN'T GO
TO THE DINNER.

33:37.288 --> 33:38.556
WE COULD JUST NOT GO.

33:38.556 --> 33:40.258
I DON'T TRUST KATE.
I DON'T TRUST HER.

33:40.258 --> 33:42.126
HEY, HEY, HEY.
EVANS DIDN'T TRUST HER.

33:42.126 --> 33:43.628
YOU TRUST ME, DON'T YOU?

33:43.628 --> 33:46.664
THE LAST TIME I TRUSTED ONE
OF YOU GUYS,

33:46.664 --> 33:48.432
I GOT DITCHED.

33:48.432 --> 33:50.468
ALL RIGHT, WELL, I'M NOT
GONNA DITCH YOU, OKAY?

33:50.468 --> 33:52.637
LOOK, I'VE KNOWN KATE
FOR A LONG TIME,

33:52.637 --> 33:55.573
AND RIGHT NOW, I DON'T TRUST HER
ANY MORE THAN YOU DO.

33:55.573 --> 33:57.542
BUT IF WE SKIP OUT
ON THIS DINNER,

33:57.542 --> 33:59.143
THEY'RE GONNA KNOW
SOMETHING'S UP.

33:59.143 --> 34:01.012
I WORKED IT INTO THE PLAN.

34:01.012 --> 34:03.014
I FOUND A ROUTE
THAT WILL CONCEAL US

34:03.014 --> 34:06.250
TILL WE GET TO THE OUTSKIRTS
OF TOWN.

34:06.250 --> 34:09.487
AND TONIGHT, AT SOME POINT
DURING THE COURSE OF DINNER,

34:09.487 --> 34:13.057
I'M GONNA EXCUSE MYSELF TO THE
BATHROOM AND CHECK FOR MIKES.

34:13.057 --> 34:15.293
WHEN I COME BACK, I WANT YOU
TO WAIT THREE MINUTES.

34:15.293 --> 34:17.461
I WANT YOU TO GET UP, I WANT YOU
TO GO TO THE SAME BATHROOM,

34:17.461 --> 34:19.196
I WANT YOU TO TAKE OUT
YOUR CHIP,

34:19.196 --> 34:20.731
AND I WANT YOU
TO LEAVE IT THERE,

34:20.731 --> 34:22.567
SOMEWHERE WHERE THEY'RE NOT
GONNA FIND IT.

34:22.567 --> 34:24.101
MAYBE BEHIND THE TOILET.

34:24.101 --> 34:27.104
OKAY.
AND THEN COME BACK
TO THE TABLE.

34:27.104 --> 34:31.442
WE FINISH DINNER,
AND THEN WE SAY GOODNIGHT.

34:31.442 --> 34:35.479
AND WE LEAVE,
AND WE GO TO THE CEMETERY,

34:35.479 --> 34:38.349
WHERE I STASHED EVANS' BAG
BEHIND THE MAUSOLEUM.

34:38.349 --> 34:40.051
WHAT IF THEY
CATCH ON TO US?

34:40.051 --> 34:41.485
NO.
NO, I MEAN IT.

34:41.485 --> 34:42.987
YOU KNOW --
HEY, HEY.

34:42.987 --> 34:46.057
THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CATCH ON TO US...

34:46.057 --> 34:49.060
AS LONG AS WE STICK
TO THE PLAN.

34:52.096 --> 34:54.231
OKAY.

34:54.231 --> 34:56.634
JUST PRETEND.

34:59.236 --> 35:02.206
WOODWORKING WAS JUST
ALWAYS MY THING.

35:02.206 --> 35:05.209
AND, UH, WHEN DID YOU
OPEN THE STORE?

35:05.209 --> 35:07.078
OH, UM,
WHEN WAS IT, HAROLD?

35:07.078 --> 35:08.512
EIGHT YEARS AGO.

35:08.512 --> 35:10.014
NO.
MM-HMM.

35:10.014 --> 35:11.248
HAS IT BEEN THAT LONG?
YEP.

35:11.248 --> 35:12.416
[CHUCKLES]
WOW.

35:12.416 --> 35:14.018
EIGHT YEARS?

35:14.018 --> 35:16.053
THAT'S ALMOST HARD
TO BELIEVE.

35:16.053 --> 35:17.388
TIME FLIES, DOESN'T IT?

35:17.388 --> 35:18.756
YEAH, SURE DOES.

35:22.259 --> 35:24.495
CAN I USE YOUR BATHROOM?

35:24.495 --> 35:26.197
OF COURSE.
IT'S RIGHT BY THE FRONT DOOR.

35:26.197 --> 35:27.565
AH, THANK YOU.

35:53.591 --> 35:55.393
[TOILET FLUSHES]

35:56.661 --> 35:59.664
HAROLD'S SPECIALTY
IS ROCKING HORSES.

35:59.664 --> 36:01.532
BACK IN PORTLAND, MY DAUGHTER
HAS A ROCKING HORSE.

36:01.532 --> 36:05.269
OH, I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU HAD A DAUGHTER.

36:05.269 --> 36:06.437
NO, I MEAN...

36:07.705 --> 36:10.341
W-W-WHAT'S HER NAME?

36:10.341 --> 36:11.776
WHAT?

36:11.776 --> 36:14.545
HAROLD, HOW DID YOU
GET INTO WOODWORKING?

36:14.545 --> 36:16.113
H-HOLD ON, ETHAN.

36:16.113 --> 36:17.248
WE WERE TALKING
ABOUT BEVERLY'S DAUGHTER.

36:21.252 --> 36:23.354
WILL YOU EXCUSE ME?

36:29.160 --> 36:30.294
[CHUCKLES LIGHTLY]

36:32.129 --> 36:33.364
[CHUCKLES]

36:41.572 --> 36:44.241
[BREATHES DEEPLY]

36:44.241 --> 36:45.609
Kate:
[Laughing]NO.

36:45.609 --> 36:47.244
YES!

36:47.244 --> 36:48.746
Harold: NO, HE DOES NOT WANT
TO HEAR IT.

36:48.746 --> 36:50.581
HE WON'T LET ME SAY THIS.
YOU'RE EMBARRASSING ME.

36:50.581 --> 36:51.982
HAROLD WON
THE HORSESHOE TOURNAMENT

36:51.982 --> 36:53.551
FOR THE SECOND YEAR
IN A ROW,

36:53.551 --> 36:54.485
AND I HAPPEN TO THINK
THAT'S SOMETHING TO BRAG ABOUT.

36:54.485 --> 36:57.021
UH, THAT CERTAINLY IS.

36:57.021 --> 36:59.423
D-DO YOU PLAY HORSESHOES,
ETHAN?

36:59.423 --> 37:01.092
HUH?
YOU KNOW, IT'S FUNNY.

37:01.092 --> 37:02.993
I-I NEVER DID
PLAY HORSESHOES.

37:06.597 --> 37:08.599
YOU KNOW, BEVERLY SEEMED
A LITTLE UNEASY.

37:08.599 --> 37:10.034
I'M GONNA GO CHECK ON HER.

37:10.034 --> 37:11.302
YOU KNOW,
SHE WAS COMPLAINING

37:11.302 --> 37:13.170
ABOUT AN UPSET STOMACH
EARLIER,

37:13.170 --> 37:14.405
BUT DON'T LET IT INTERRUPT
YOUR DINNER.

37:14.405 --> 37:15.573
WELL, I'M ALREADY UP.

37:15.573 --> 37:17.274
NO,
I'M GONNA GO CHECK ON HER.

37:17.274 --> 37:18.576
YEAH.

37:18.576 --> 37:21.112
IF I DON'T, I'LL NEVER HEAR
THE END OF IT.

37:21.112 --> 37:22.379
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN,
HAROLD?

37:22.379 --> 37:24.515
YOU KNOW THAT, YEAH.
[CHUCKLES]

37:24.515 --> 37:27.384
BUT I APPRECIATE YOUR CONCERN.
SIT DOWN, SIT DOWN.

37:39.196 --> 37:41.031
[SIGHS]

37:41.031 --> 37:44.034
Ethan:
I'M SORRY, LOOK...

37:44.034 --> 37:45.369
BEVERLY APOLOGIZES.

37:45.369 --> 37:47.638
IT SEEMS
THAT STOMACH AILMENT

37:47.638 --> 37:49.240
HAS REALLY GOTTEN
THE BETTER OF HER.

37:49.240 --> 37:51.308
OH, NO.
I HOPE IT WASN'T MY COOKING.

37:51.308 --> 37:53.043
OH, GOD, NO.
NO, NO, NO, NO.

37:53.043 --> 37:54.678
SHE'S OUTSIDE.
I'M JUST GONNA --

37:54.678 --> 37:56.347
I'M GONNA WALK HER
ON HOME.

37:56.347 --> 37:58.048
OH, OF COURSE, YEAH.
YOU SHOULD DEFINITELY --

37:58.048 --> 37:59.283
OH, UH, CAN I GIVE YOU A PIECE
OF PIE FOR THE ROAD?

37:59.283 --> 38:00.651
UH, OH, NO, NO, NO,
THANKS.

38:00.651 --> 38:03.220
BUT LET'S DO THIS AGAIN
REAL SOON, OKAY? THANKS.

38:03.220 --> 38:05.689
SURE.
DEFINITELY.

38:05.689 --> 38:08.292
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]

38:08.292 --> 38:09.460
[SIGHS]

38:09.460 --> 38:12.263
YOU THINK
THEY'RE GONNA RUN?

38:12.263 --> 38:14.098
ABSOLUTELY.

38:19.428 --> 38:21.748
PSST, HEY.
LISTEN TO ME.

38:21.748 --> 38:22.926
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

38:22.926 --> 38:25.124
[Voice breaking]I TOLD THEM
THAT I HAD A DAUGHTER.

38:25.124 --> 38:27.193
I SLIPPED.
I'M NOT A GOOD LIAR.

38:27.193 --> 38:28.761
THEY COULD SEE IT
IN MY FACE.

38:28.761 --> 38:29.896
OKAY, IT'S OKAY.
I SAID --

38:29.896 --> 38:32.565
SHH, IT'S OKAY.
ALL RIGHT.

38:32.565 --> 38:33.700
LET'S JUST WALK CALM.

38:33.700 --> 38:34.901
OKAY.

38:34.901 --> 38:37.103
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH THE CHIP?

38:37.103 --> 38:39.138
I LEFT IT IN THE BATHROOM
LIKE YOU SAID.

38:39.138 --> 38:41.240
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

38:41.240 --> 38:43.276
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU HAD A DAUGHTER.

38:43.276 --> 38:45.945
YEAH.
SHE'S SIX YEARS OLD.

38:45.945 --> 38:48.114
SHE LIVES IN PORTLAND
WITH MY MOM.

38:48.114 --> 38:51.617
LISTEN,
PROMISE ME ONE THING.
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

38:51.617 --> 38:52.985
IF I DON'T MAKE IT
OUT OF HERE,

38:52.985 --> 38:54.253
JUST PROMISE ME YOU'LL --

38:54.253 --> 38:55.922
HEY, HEY, HEY,
NONE OF THAT.
GO TO HER.

38:55.922 --> 38:57.623
WE'RE GONNA MAKE IT
OUT OF HERE.

38:57.623 --> 38:58.758
[TELEPHONES RINGING]

38:58.758 --> 39:00.626
OH, GOD.
WHAT IS IT?

39:00.626 --> 39:02.628
THAT'S HOW IT STARTED
WHEN THEY KILLED BILL.

39:02.628 --> 39:05.798
THE TELEPHONES.
ALL RIGHT.

39:05.798 --> 39:06.999
ALL THE TELEPHONES!

39:06.999 --> 39:09.068
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

39:09.068 --> 39:10.737
Woman: COME ON!

39:10.737 --> 39:12.505
Man:
WE'RE LOOKING OUT FOR THEM.

39:12.505 --> 39:14.107
GRAB MY HAND.
DON'T LET GO.

39:14.107 --> 39:16.709
[RINGING AND SHOUTING
CONTINUE]

39:16.709 --> 39:18.745
THEY'RE GONNA KILL US!

39:18.745 --> 39:20.179
DON'T LET GO OF MY HAND.

39:20.179 --> 39:21.714
ALL RIGHT, SHH.
OKAY.

39:21.714 --> 39:24.183
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

39:24.183 --> 39:27.754
GET TO THE CEMETERY.
GET THE MAP.

39:27.754 --> 39:29.155
I WON'T LEAVE WITHOUT YOU.

39:29.155 --> 39:31.758
GO AND GET YOUR DAUGHTER!
I'LL DISTRACT THEM.

39:31.758 --> 39:34.594
Man: THEY RAN THAT WAY!

39:34.594 --> 39:37.897
Man #2: THAT GUY WAS LAST SEEN
BY THE BALLINGERS!

39:37.897 --> 39:39.966
Man #3:
THEY'VE BEEN SPOTTED!

39:39.966 --> 39:41.968
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

39:41.968 --> 39:43.669
[RINGING CONTINUES]

39:43.669 --> 39:46.139
RIGHT?
YEAH.

39:46.139 --> 39:47.707
Woman:
A MALE AND FEMALE.

39:47.707 --> 39:49.575
HEY. HEY!

39:49.575 --> 39:50.877
WHERE IS SHE?

39:54.514 --> 39:58.217
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

40:00.987 --> 40:03.856
[PANTING]

40:08.628 --> 40:10.897
[SOBBING]

40:10.897 --> 40:12.131
RIGHT THERE, RIGHT THERE!

40:12.131 --> 40:13.933
Man:
DO YOU SEE HIM?
YEAH.

40:16.803 --> 40:18.171
[BREATHING UNEVENLY]

40:19.639 --> 40:22.141
Man #4: WE'LL MEET THEM
BACK AT THE RENDEZVOUS.

40:22.141 --> 40:23.776
[INDISTINCT TALKING]

40:23.776 --> 40:25.812
[GASPS]

40:32.285 --> 40:34.720
[GASPS]

40:46.065 --> 40:49.735
[DOORKNOB RATTLES]

40:49.735 --> 40:51.737
[SHOUTING]

40:58.711 --> 41:00.713
[PANTING]

41:02.949 --> 41:06.018
BEFORE WE BEGIN,

41:06.018 --> 41:09.655
I'D LIKE TO THANK EVERYONE
FOR BEING HERE.

41:09.655 --> 41:11.724
I'D LIKE EVERYONE
TO TAKE A MOMENT

41:11.724 --> 41:14.093
TO THANK KATE
AND HAROLD BALLINGER

41:14.093 --> 41:16.996
FOR DOING THEIR CIVIC DUTY

41:16.996 --> 41:19.732
AND BRINGING THIS WOMAN
TO JUSTICE!

41:19.732 --> 41:22.969
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

41:35.014 --> 41:38.150
BEVERLY BROWN TRIED TO LEAVE.

41:38.150 --> 41:39.785
SHE DISCUSSED THE PAST.

41:39.785 --> 41:41.654
OH, NO.

41:54.033 --> 41:57.537
AS I'VE SAID
MANY TIMES BEFORE...

41:59.805 --> 42:01.541
[GRUNTS]

42:01.541 --> 42:06.579
...IT IS NOT JUST MY JOB
TO KEEP THIS TOWN SAFE.

42:06.579 --> 42:08.214
[SCREAMS]

42:09.916 --> 42:11.250
IT'S EVERYBODY'S!

42:13.920 --> 42:15.555
Man: JUSTICE!

42:15.555 --> 42:17.056
Woman:
SHE DESERVED IT!

42:20.226 --> 42:23.563
[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]

42:28.200 --> 42:29.769
Man:
WAY TO GO, SHERIFF!

42:29.769 --> 42:33.506
Sheriff Pope:
WE CANNOT TOLERATE PEOPLE

42:33.506 --> 42:34.974
WHO DON'T PLAY BY THE RULES!
